    <div class="faq-a" id="who-are-the-best-seo-experts-to-follow-on-linkedin"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The strongest SEO experts to follow on LinkedIn in 2026 are Lily Ray for core update analysis, Kevin Indig for SaaS and product-led SEO strategy, Aleyda Solis for international and technical SEO, Mike King for deep technical and patent analysis, and Barry Schwartz for breaking algorithm news. For content strategy, Ann Handley and Ross Simmonds consistently deliver original, actionable frameworks. The right list for you depends on your role — technical SEOs, agency owners, in-house marketers, and content strategists all have different people who will be most relevant to their daily work.</p></div></div>
